Question 2: Proration Calculation Method
FR-003 requires prorated charges/credits for mid-cycle plan changes, but the calculation method isn't specified. This is critical for financial accuracy and customer expectations.
Recommended: Option A (Daily proration)
This is the industry standard for SaaS billing because:
Most accurate and fair representation of usage
Matches how Stripe and most payment processors handle proration
Customers expect daily precision for plan changes
Prevents disputes over "unfair" partial month calculations
Option	Description
A	Daily proration - Calculate charges/credits based on exact number of days used at each plan level (e.g., 15 days at old rate, 15 days at new rate for mid-month change)
